version_description: These are the only chords for this song on the internet.
Cadd9 can also be used in the prechorus. these chord changes an be quite fast so listen to the song :).
This was tabbed based on this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NaE0_hgSwXc.
Precise and accurate chords. Walk-ups in the choruses.
No other version has the fingerstyle parts right in a hybrid chord/TAB format. This one meets that criteria PLUS fits on two printed pages for those that want to add to their songbook
An alternate version of a song that was not in the UG database. Simple and able to receive better corrections.
